# HTML project assembly

Builder-owned routes, fragments and project artifacts.

## Contract

- Input: compiled modules, backend settings and builder metadata
- Output: HTML route artifacts, tracked assets and cleanup policy
- Decides: route layout, fragment merge, backend selection, asset emission
- Must not decide: frontend semantics, HIR shape, target code generation
- Invariant: the HTML builder owns the shared page-fragment plan for both HTML-JS and HTML-Wasm

## Main paths

- `src/projects/html_project/html_project_builder.rs`
- `src/projects/html_project/js_path.rs`
- `src/projects/html_project/wasm/`

